OL,3,CRobot performs first simulated
OL,4,Coperation in space
OL,6,FA tiny robot surgeon that lives aboard
OL,7,Fthe International Space Station has
OL,8,Fcompleted its first ever simulated
OL,9,Foperation in zero gravity.
OL,11,FSpeaking to CNN, developers of the
OL,12,Ftechnology said the spaceMIRA - which
OL,13,Fstands for Miniaturised in Vivo
OL,14,FRobotic Assistant - performed several
OL,15,Foperations on simulated tissue while
OL,16,Fbeing controlled by surgeons around
OL,17,F250 miles below, in Nebraska, USA.
