OL,3,CRobot performs first simulated
OL,4,Coperation in space
OL,6,FThe operation could mark a step
OL,7,Fforward in developing technology that
OL,8,Fcould help during long-term space
OL,9,Ftravel and establish medical care in
OL,10,Fremote areas of Earth.
OL,12,FIt comes as the US continues to push
OL,13,Ftowards exploration in deeper space.
OL,15,FHow does the robot work?
OL,17,FThe robot weighs just under a
OL,18,Fkilogram, and its compact microwave-
OL,19,Fsize design makes it ideal for space
OL,20,Ftravel.
