OL,3,CRobot performs first simulated
OL,4,Coperation in space
OL,6,FIt makes use of two arms to mimic the
OL,7,Fmovements of a human, a left arm to
OL,8,Fgrasp items and a right arm to cut,
OL,9,Fsays Shane Farritor, cofounder and
OL,10,Fchief technology officer at Virtual
OL,11,FIncision, the startup that created
OL,12,FspaceMIRA.
OL,14,FSpeaking to CNN, Mr Farritor said: "It
OL,15,Fgives smaller hands and eyes to the
OL,16,Fsurgeon (on Earth) and allows them to
OL,17,Fperform a lot of procedures minimally
OL,18,Finvasively."
