OL,3,CRobot performs first simulated
OL,4,Coperation in space
OL,6,FSpaceMIRA hitched a ride on a SpaceX
OL,7,FFalcon 9 rocket on January 30 from
OL,8,FFlorida's Cape Canaveral Space Force
OL,9,FStation and arrived at the space
OL,10,Fstation on February 1.
OL,12,FThe robot is set to return to Earth in
OL,13,Fthe Spring.
OL,15,FFindings from its journey could also
OL,16,Fbe valuable for surgery options on
OL,17,FEarth, such as helping in rural
OL,18,Flocations or even on military
OL,19,Fbattlefields.
