OL,3,CRobot performs first simulated
OL,4,Coperation in space
OL,6,F"There are a lot of places in the US
OL,7,Fthat don't have access to specialists,
OL,8,Fand if you could perform telesurgery
OL,9,Flike this, where you could have an
OL,10,Fexpert dial in from a larger city into
OL,11,Fa rural area and assist with some
OL,12,Fsurgical care, I think that's got huge
OL,13,Fadvantages," Mr Farritor said.
